{
  "name": "RPlog_A_Caspian_House_Warming_Party",
  "title": "A Caspian House-Warming Party",
  "summary": "Di'anCecht and Jessalyn host an intimate house-warming dinner at their riverside cottage in Plaxton City, Caspar, welcoming Piper and her companion Kuxli along with Avalyshaar, Grei, and the visibly unwell Lotus. The evening's warmth curdles as Avalyshaar excuses herself in distress and Lotus, pregnant and weakened by a recent illness, collapses unconscious before the meal can be served. Piper fetches a nurse, who diagnoses a stress-induced collapse and warns of slightly concerning readings around the baby, urging Lotus to rest and seek a proper exam. Lotus recovers enough to insist on going home despite the hosts' protests, and the party breaks up with the guests departing into the late night. The gathering ends on a note of quiet worry rather than celebration.",
